Constructs a new SourceInfoComparison.

Parameters:
cardId - A String containing the identifier of the Card whose SourceInfo differences are being described.
typeChanged - true if the type of the SourceInfo is different between the two versions; false otherwise.
referenceChanged - true if the reference for the SourceInfo is different between the two versions; false otherwise.
dateChanged - true if the date and time associated with the SourceInfo is different between the two versions; false otherwise.
descriptionChanged - true if the description of the SourceInfo is different between the two versions; false otherwise.
